.DT
set_counter
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
set_counter

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_counter -  This method sets the current message counter.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_counter(int x)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^x%^RESET%^ - the new value for the counter

.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/folder_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the current message counter.  This will return a
message if the counter was not valid.  This should be called in the
event that a recovery is needed if the counter screws up.
.EP

